                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-334-off1717 t18310908-334-crimeloc1720"></join>, the prisoner came and took the necklace off; I cried Stop thief! and ran up the street - he turned towards Churchpassage, and then the Policeman took him; I lost sight of him for about a minute, while he turned the corner, but am sure of his person - there were two others with him, who ran another away.</p>
